  <brief_title>Clinical Evaluation of the SportWelding FijiAnchor速 in Hand and Hand Wrist Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Clinical Evaluation of the Bioabsorbable SportWelding FijiAnchor速 for Ligament Repair of the Hand and Hand Wrist</official_title>
