  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Having a condition requiring (re)fixation or (re)construction of ligaments in the hand
             or hand wrist

          -  Being able to comprehend, sign, and date the written informed consent form (ICF)); and

          -  Being able to visit the hospital to be examined the repaired region after the
             procedure.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Having serious concomitant disease

          -  Being pregnant

          -  Having the control hand not suitable to serve as comparator
      </textblock>
